label: Darwin Core type vocabulary terms
description: This term list was formerly used to indicate the type of Darwin Core resources.  It was deprecated in favor of class terms in the core terms namespace.

description: This obsolete term list described curatorial terms.

description: This obsolete term list described core terms in the vocabulary.

description: This obsolete term list described geospatial terms.

label: Obsolete Darwin Core terms that are not in a TDWG namespace
description: This list includes terms formerly cosidered to be a part of Darwin Core, but that are not part of a namespace controlled by TDWG  (http://rs.tdwg.org/).

label: Core terms defined by Darwin Core
description: This term list includes all currently valid terms that have been defined in the core Darwin Core namespace dwc:.  To comment on this schema, please create a new issue in https://github.com/tdwg/dwc/issues

label: TDWG utility terms
description: This list includes terms necessary to describe various TDWG vocabularies.

label: Darwin Core IRI-value Term Analogs
description: The terms on this list are intended to be used with IRI values

description: This term list includes all currently valid terms that have been defined in the core Audiovisual Core namespace ac:.

Its terms are not dereferenceable.

label: XMP namespace terms from the XMP specification borrowed by Audiovisual Core

Its terms are not dereferenceable.
